Mindscribe – AI-Powered Thought-to-Text System
🚀 Mindscribe is an AI-powered web application that analyzes neural wave images and converts them into text-based thoughts. This project aims to help individuals with speech impairments or disabilities express their thoughts effortlessly.

🌟 Features
✅ Image-to-Thought AI – Upload a neural wave image & generate text.
✅ Emotion & Cognitive State Detection – AI predicts feelings & intentions.
✅ DeepSeek RI API Integration – Advanced AI processing for text output.
✅ Secure Authentication – Login/signup via Supabase Auth.
✅ Cloud Storage – Saves processed thoughts securely.
✅ Customizable UI – Dark/Light mode, font adjustments.

🛠 Tech Stack
Frontend:
Next.js (React Framework)
Tailwind CSS + ShadCN (Modern UI components)
Supabase Auth (User authentication & database)
Backend:
Flask (Python-based backend)
Supabase DB (Database storage for thoughts)
DeepSeek RI API (AI processing for neural wave images)
