📌 How It Works (Step-by-Step)
1️⃣ User uploads an image of neural wave signals.
2️⃣ AI (DeepSeek RI API) processes the image and extracts cognitive insights.
3️⃣ Text output appears, displaying emotions, thoughts, or intentions.
4️⃣ Users can edit, save, or export the generated thoughts.

